reviewText: Waste of money no body take off there clothes
Another great film from the King.

This is my favorite roughie.  It's a re-edit of "Disgruntled Employee" which I find to be far superior (and the original cut was glorious!).  This movie also has a re-edit of "Rap Sucks" which makes this more of a double feature.  It also has bloopers which help one to decompress after watching such a tension-filled movie like "Do Unto Otthers"  Angelina Leigh gives a stand-out performance - probably the best acting in a rape scene.  I know that might seem like a demented thing to state, but low budget erotic horror sometimes has damsels who cry like little brats who had their toys taken away by scolding parents.  I like Bill Zebub's surreal erotic horror - the movies that don't have much dialogue (only the mightmarish scenes) but this barrative is one of the best, topped only by his "Crippled by Desire" movie that is part of the "50 Shades of Scarlett" double feature.  All i cna say is "MORE Angelina Leigh, please!"
This movie and all the other movies from Bill zebub are nothing but garbage. Do not buy any of his movies. He should be hung for making such trash.
